title: NFS MW - UC HD MOD (2012) (Setup)
description:
WELCOME TO NEED FOR SPEED : MOST WANTED - UNDERGROUND CARBON HD MOD (2012)

This is a mod I made back in the end of 2012. It's a heavily modified version of NFS Most Wanted 2005, which contains features from NFS Underground (1&2), NFS Carbon and NFS Most Wanted (2005&2012). If you play the whole storyline from the beggining you might find a bug with invisible cars or just visible wheels with no chasis. This can be easily fixed just by jumping to a safe house and then resuming gameplay. Have fun :) and please seed !!
